{"tid":2255474,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件做gym時on9/玩命事件","createTime":"2020-10-23T14:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T03:23:54.000Z","uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5677a1807fa03bb873643283ea0c38504a97baca","tid":2255474,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"讀書嗰陣暑假無聊得濟玩加過啲康文署器械健體訓練班 要上成個月 唔知total 15堂定幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾堂玩部單車機同跑步機 為咗想睇心跳極限可以幾多 試過瘋狂咁踩部單車機 踩到見住心跳上到過190 最高唔知上到197定198<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要唔只一堂玩到過190 跟住教練見到我個心跳咁高即刻俾佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得19X心跳維持咗5分鐘左右 嗰陣臨落堂 一落堂嗰下行出吓對腳好似浮吓浮吓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727350b10c6703c1a6846785d6420545f07f5ba4","tid":2255474,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"有幾玩命 過200好平常"},{"pid":"eed04dccb00f2aeebe308cce1f584f9685983734","tid":2255474,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"有幾玩命 過300好平常"},{"pid":"9a203128dea856618e4fc32f9cbdca1c67e01619","tid":2255474,"uid":258784,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"有幾玩命 過400好平常"},{"pid":"ca4631c45ae8464e80bfb4e90e52ede22ae29998","tid":2255474,"uid":77355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"有幾玩命 過500好平常"},{"pid":"41e5b7f569ef0c3757752c59dec9b9596f25cd29","tid":2255474,"uid":280681,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"我之前跑到個心真係跳左出黎 好彩執得返冇事"},{"pid":"7d920b8a76e437d43adf9487bc840dd8b9ea2878","tid":2255474,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/TwNrZK3gGcJn87Ls9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.li